Page_0: "Zaya, I have bestowed upon you the final piece of crystal in my possession. For now being too old and having no use for it, I believe it shall be wielded with a great power in your hands. This shard will take the noxious gas of the natural land and will turn it into the volatile fumes of the Maw's underbelly. Harmless by itself, the air contained within your arrow crystals will ignite near any open flame, reigning down the fire of the Woodsie Lord upon all within its wake.

-Malak"